{"tid":428434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［美國智庫］中國計劃暗殺「台灣領導人」","createTime":"2017-10-08T05:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T06:03:48.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1e79fb7e7bce5904539437d3ef003c62487622","tid":428434,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國智庫「2049計劃室」研究員易思安在新書《中國侵略威脅》中提及，中國已擬定一份「2020年攻台的秘密計畫」，引發各界議論，雖然他在接受媒體訪問時強調，這個說法是引用台灣國防部2013年的國防白皮書，但易思安也指出，解放軍內部文件揭露，不排除會針對台灣高階領導人以及領導者的家屬發動「斬首戰」。<br />\n<br />\n易思安在新書《中國侵略威脅》中揭露，中國解放軍已擬訂一份2020年攻台的秘密計畫，在近期引發討論。不過，他近日在接受《美國之音》訪問時強調，他是引用台灣國防部2013年的國防白皮書，且「2020共軍攻台」並不是他這本書的重點，而是想表達台灣政府雖然小心保守，但中國還是隨時想侵略台灣。<br />\n<br />\n易思安在接受《三立新聞》訪問時則說，中共其實還沒準備好攻打台灣，「其實對於能不能順利攻打台灣他們是很悲觀的」，因此，目前並沒有確切攻打台灣的時間表。<br />\n<br />\n不過，易思安也透露，從一些解放軍的內部資料來看，中國的特工人員可能會收買台灣的領導人或家人，甚至進行暗殺行動。易思安說，他看到這些資料非常震驚，因為中國對台的作戰計畫是很野蠻而且很血腥的！<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2216497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2216497&d=4XQIVCbeeCMwHoKAx8ePbdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=dc14c40a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2216497&h=9972e556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2216497</a><br />\n---<br />\n邪惡中共計劃曝光"},{"pid":"c53d95e94d5e11275124487d49ea59811801cc5b","tid":428434,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:18:33.000Z","msg":"咁我又信喎， 台仔出名25仔<br />\n求其搵個淫虫威脅住佢就得"},{"pid":"c70cd9134887e9317f45534103803dc65f047a0b","tid":428434,"uid":42764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:34:34.000Z","msg":"攻擊其家屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n道德撚呢?"},{"pid":"db81f4bedb05b96c49b6b32a66e0dd33dc2942cc","tid":428434,"uid":91721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:36:50.000Z","msg":"反中亂台<br />\n殺無赦!<br />\n<br />\n喂JR我幫你講埋你啲對白啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4e759ac7903e992ec16bdf213a9fd4dd2884b4","tid":428434,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:39:59.000Z","msg":"支那賤畜對所謂自己人就兇狠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7acba4e86898aefbd76fbbf8237181462786082f","tid":428434,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"剎咗2房東有鬼用咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1939d168beaa735c65018997fe8672be7337d12d","tid":428434,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b969b21f9914868f4acdae2c080804849e0478","tid":428434,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"英文危險了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過被亡國的命運是不會改變的哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e2d4ef8d4bc08107a2020e8759aadb14f2712f","tid":428434,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}